      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">MAURITIUS ¶ MUNICIPALITY ¶ OF ¶ PORT-LOUIS ¶ Town-Hall...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">M96.02.06</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Charles Thomy Pitot to [Mayor of Melbourne]</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 950, unit 637, VPRS 3181/P Town Clerk's file series 1, VA 511 Melbourne City Council, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS annotation in an unknown hand: '14/3/96 Baron Von Mueller Mr Guilfoyle &amp; Mr Perrin } enclg co [copy?] &amp; asking their asstce to comply [with] request.' </p>
               </note>MAURITIUS</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">MUNICIPALITY</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">OF</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">PORT-LOUIS</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; font-style: italic; "
               xml:lang="en">Town-Hall</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">6th February 1896</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It being my intention to have our public gardens and other dispo[ss]ible places planted with Eucalyptus, on the largest possible extent, with a view to remedy the effect of malarial fever in Port-Louis, I venture to have recourse to your kindness &amp; to request that you will be good enough to procure me a variety of seeds of that valuable plant which, in your opinion may suit best for our climate &amp; for the object I have in view.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am advised to cultivate principally the species Robusta &amp; Citriodora — I need not add that I will be very happy to reciprocate should you wish to be favoured with some seeds of our tropical plants.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Trusting that I am not inflicting too much trouble upon you please accept my anticipated thank<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">sic</seg>.</p>
               </note> and</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Believe me,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Yours faithfully;</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>C <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>E. Thomy Pitot</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mayor of Port-Louis.<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">there is an annot. on the front of the file that is too pale to read: 'Forward with the intimation that seeds [are … … …] of Baron v Mueller. ? and copy of Baron's letter'. It seems that they replied to M on 14/3 and Guilfoyle and Perrin on 17/3. Also: 'R[ecd] 27.6.96'.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">His Worship </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">The Mayor of Melbourne<note xml:id="ftn5" type="footnote" n="5">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">It appears that all of the correspondence about this matter was conducted through the Mayor of Melbourne. A reply was sent by W. Guilfoyle, including a list of the seeds sent (no. 1237, unit 637, VPRS 3181/P, Public Record Office, Victoria).</p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </div>
